HEADWORD: Latitat
<hw>Lat"i*tat</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., he lies
hid.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A writ based upon the
presumption that the person summoned was hiding.</def>
